+ : new feature
- : deprecated feature
* : bugfix or changed code
Bug numbers are references to bugs in http://www.achievo.org/bugzilla
[names] are references to people in the AUTHORS file.

Changes in Carlease 1.0.0
-------------------------
+ Initial version
+ Added current owner display to the leasecar admin page. [Guido]
+ Added translations for fuel types. [Guido]
+ Made lease sum visible in leasecar admin page. [Guido]
+ Added lpg to fuel's [Guido]
+ Added posibility to add multiple insurances per car, each having it's
  ownrisk and description. [Guido]
* Made status field obligatory and removed "empty" option. [Guido]
* Fixed translation of damage. [Guido]
